Internal flow of Claude
  --Prompt - input that we are providing to the LLM
  --Tokenization - splitting the text     example - Java |is | a| programming
  --Embeddings - converting text into vector - machine understandable language
  --Tranformer layers(each layers) - example ->
             teacher correcting the essay -- layer 1 - Basic, layer 2 - grammar, layer 3 - sentence meaning, layer 4 - deep context
      -read all words
      -check relationships
      -better understanding
      -pass from better understanding layer to next layer
  --Attention Mechanism - AI focuses important words to understand the meaning.
      human understands - The animal didn't cross the road because it was tired.
                        - here "it" - "animal" --> human brain knows that automatically.. like wise AI gather the important word for Attention mechanism
  --Output


